Revision history for html2dbk
=============================

0.03 Wed 22 March 2006
----------------------

  * (22 Mar 2006) external stylesheet
  	Enabled the use of an external stylesheet in place of the built-in
  default one.

  * (22 Mar 2006) doc fix
  	Forgot to document the chapter title change!

  * (22 Mar 2006) html and fixes
  	- chapter title comes from <title> tag
  	- new --html option uses the LibXML parse HTML facility
  	- fixed bugs with tables

0.02 Tue 21 March 2006
----------------------

  * (21 Mar 2006) tweaks
  	- make the distribution be the html2dbk not the module name.
  	- added a bit more documentation.

0.01 Tue 21 March 2006
----------------------

  * (21 Mar 2006) initial checkin
